org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.graph.spatial.io

Class VertexDegreeColorizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.graph.spatial.io.VertexDegreeColorizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Colorizable

    public class VertexDegreeColorizer
extends Object
implements Colorizable
    A VertexDegreeColorizer colorizes vertices according to their degree. The colors are out of a continous color spectrum white-green-red-blue scaled to the degree distribution.
    Author:
    jillenberger
